fields.Title: ICE / ACELE
fields.Description: Lead-in to the speedfreaks, out on the ice

fields.Title: Acele: ""So should you.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "So should you."

fields.Title: Authority: "Odd. Something about the way she sa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Odd. Something about the way she says it makes you think she's not bothered by any of the cop-show questioning.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""It's supposed to become, like, a c..."]
You: ""I think it's the plight of the wor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think it's the plight of the working class."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm pretty sure I've got issues wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm pretty sure I've got issues with our young women kneeling in the snow with this *cosmopolitan* racket going on in the background." (Nod towards the tent.)
fields.Alternate1: "I'm pretty sure I've got issues with our young women kneeling in the snow with this *cosmopolitan* racket going on in the background." (Nod towards the stage.)

fields.Title: You: "The tape recorder lies on the ice l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The tape recorder lies on the ice like a discarded toy. Pick it up.

fields.Title: You: ""Um... Kim? What are you doing?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Um... Kim? What are you doing?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Tryin'a score some *dope*, man. Tr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tryin'a score some *dope*, man. Tryin'a score some smack -- you got any?" He hops from one foot to the other.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""*Diamorphine*, girl. Quit clownin'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Diamorphine*, girl. Quit clownin'. We need a hook-up for that D..." He breathes in through his teeth.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm once again reminded of how Con..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm once again reminded of how Contact Mike rose from the slums of Saint-Batiste to the top of the boxing world, overcoming adversity and serious brain trauma. Nothing is coming -- nothing he wouldn't knock out in three rounds. The real fight is for the right attitude."

fields.Title: Empathy: "It's real. Tell her."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's real. Tell her.

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "A silver bird... feels strangely fa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A silver bird... feels strangely familiar. Was it an expression? And if yes, then for what? Then your mind slips and the thought is gone.

fields.Title: Acele: ""... but I shouldn't, really. I hav..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "... but I shouldn't, really. I have stuff planned for tomorrow. Gotta run around, try to make some money."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Right.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Right."

fields.Title: You: ""I am the police. You would do well..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am the police. You would do well to avoid this kind of language with me."

fields.Title: Perception: "Her hair is dyed blonde, with dark..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her hair is dyed blonde, with dark roots showing. Most men wouldn't exactly call her pretty -- there is a manliness to her. A coarseness.

fields.Title: Authority: "You're saying it really loud, but i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're saying it really loud, but it's not coming out right. Maybe add more indignation?

fields.Title: Acele: ""Wait...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait..."

fields.Title: Acele: "The words are stuck in your throat...."
fields.Dialogue Text: The words are stuck in your throat. All that comes out is tears, pouring down your face. The young woman has kept her eyes trained on her wires, waiting for the lecture to end, but now she hears sobbing...

fields.Title: You: ""I got shot in the leg." (Point at..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I got shot in the leg." (Point at your limb.)

fields.Title: You: ""But Contact Mike is --""
fields.Dialogue Text: "But Contact Mike is --"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, well... actually, it's not i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, well... actually, it's not important. I actually wanted to thank you."

fields.Title: Acele: ""What do you mean?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""It was a stupid idea and I'm still..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It was a stupid idea and I'm still disappointed *I* came up with it."

fields.Title: You: ""You said eating me? There's nothin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You said eating me? There's nothing eating me."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["ice.acele_emp_success_psych_session"] == true  and  Variable["ice.acele_ended_crying_in_front_of_her"] == false  and  Variable["ice.acele_psych_session_done"] == false

fields.Title: Acele: "A shaggy-looking girl in her late t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A shaggy-looking girl in her late teens or early twenties kneels on the ice with an electronic contraption in her hand. Hearing you approach, she looks up.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Huh?" She looks up at you, distrac..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Huh?" She looks up at you, distracted.
fields.Alternate1: "Huh?"

fields.Title: You: ""I should -- and I do." (Point at y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I should -- and I do." (Point at your hat.)
fields.Alternate1: "But I am!" (Point at your hat.)

fields.Title: You: ""I mean: we get drinks -- and we al..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I mean: we get drinks -- and we also get drugs."

fields.Title: Acele: ""You sure?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You sure?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Or, or... I'm just gonna put this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Or, or... I'm just gonna put this out there -- are you sure you're not having *chick* issues, with some chick?"

fields.Title: You: ""They were written in a woman's han..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They were written in a woman's hand. And oh boy did reading them make me not feel good."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Really?" She appears to believe yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Really?" She appears to believe you. "You seem pretty upset about this *chica*... are you sure you don't remember anything about her?"

fields.Title: You: ""What's there to know in this shit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's there to know in this shit hole, anyway?"

fields.Title: You: ""Alright, I had some questions for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Alright, I had some questions for you."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yeah, man..." The lieutenant sudde..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, man..." The lieutenant suddenly appears to your right with his collar popped *insanely* high.

fields.Title: Acele: ""What's... 'the D'?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's... 'the D'?"

fields.Title: You: ""What is going on?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What is going on?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I know." Her teeth rattle. She tak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know." Her teeth rattle. She takes the device from you and places it in her lap. "I'll stick to it."

fields.Title: You: ""The dark.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The dark."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Oh, really?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, really?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I swear to god, I will always wear..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I swear to god, I will always wear a hat from now on."

fields.Title: Acele: ""What is it?" She listens intently."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What is it?" She listens intently.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Just no?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Just no?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Actually just one wire, I picked o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Actually just one wire, I picked on it till the braiding came loose. The wire leads to a contact microphone."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Man, I have no clue, either.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Man, I have no clue, either."

fields.Title: You: ""Uh... we'll be back later." [Leave..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh... we'll be back later." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Acele: ""So, the thing that's been eating y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So, the thing that's been eating you... is rich people not having enough money?"
fields.Alternate1: "So, the thing that's got you crying in front of strangers... is rich people not having enough money?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, I'm sorry." She nods. "Might..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, I'm sorry." She nods. "Might be for the best to keep that shit forgotten, actually. Just my opinion. If it itches, don't scratch."

fields.Title: Empathy: "The device is cold to the touch. An..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The device is cold to the touch. An angular "Omicron" logo adorns the yellow plastic cover. Underneath you see a reel of tape rolling. You put the device back on the ice.
fields.Alternate1: The device feels light. An angular "Omicron" logo adorns the yellow plastic cover. Underneath you see a reel of tape rolling. You put the device back on the floor.

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Interesting."
fields.Dialogue Text: Interesting.

fields.Title: You: ""Goddamnit, why's there no one to d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Goddamnit, why's there no one to drink with by the seaside!" (Raise your hands in lamentation.)

fields.Title: Acele: ""Like what?"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Like what?

fields.Title: Acele: ""Sorry, I have stuff planned for to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry, I have stuff planned for tomorrow. Gotta run around, try to make some money."

fields.Title: You: "Start crying."
fields.Dialogue Text: Start crying.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Three figures on the spring ice. On..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Three figures on the spring ice. One, a shortish man, is standing with his shoulders slightly hunched. Another, a young woman, tries her best to ignore the third, a middle-aged man with bloated cheeks, who's screaming at her with all his might...

fields.Title: You: "The tape recorder lies on the woode..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The tape recorder lies on the wooden floorboards like a discarded toy. Pick it up.

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["ice.acele_tape_recorder_idea"] == true  and  Variable["church.ravers_inside_church"] == true  and  Variable["ice.acele_emp_on_ice_succeeded"] == false

fields.Title: You: ""I guess... there is something... t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I guess... there is something... that's been making my life hell."

fields.Title: You: ""I'd like to know more about your a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'd like to know more about your associates..."
fields.Alternate1: "*Now* can you tell me about your associates?"

fields.Title: You: ""That's nice to hear. You kids are..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's nice to hear. You kids are good these days."

fields.Title: You: ""Never mind, I don't really want to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Never mind, I don't really want to hear any of this."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Good for you. Now, was there anyth..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good for you. Now, was there anything else on your mind?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah... I was kinda hoping you'd e..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah... I was kinda hoping you'd end that mess before we got going. It feels like I've been slowly turning dad-wise, into a corrupt business-person.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Thanks for helping us out. My asso..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks for helping us out. My associates and I are settling in here nicely. Even found some new associates." She turns back to her work, whistling softly...

fields.Title: Acele: ""Recording the audio coming through..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Recording the audio coming through the wooden framework. I bet it's pretty cool. Creaks and stuff. Sounds like when you're underwater, you know?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I'm listening." She puts the conta..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm listening." She puts the contact mic down and props herself up a bit, waiting for you to speak.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""Okay... but you'll still let us kn..."]
Acele: ""Oh, I didn't notice that.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, I didn't notice that."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, well..." She tries to think..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, well..." She tries to think of something to say. "Look man, fuck the hat."

fields.Title: You: "(Say it again louder, she might not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Say it again louder, she might not have heard you over the wind.) "DO YOU WANT TO PARTY?!"

fields.Title: You: ""I mean: we buy drinks, and, right..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I mean: we buy drinks, and, right there in the liquor store, we get those bad boys in us, and then *you* tell *me* what you mean when *you* say *party*!"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""... and neither have you. Had you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "... and neither have you. Had you let me in on the script of this play before you performed it, I could have gone along. As it stands, the entire line of questioning has been compromised."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Believe me, dude, it's better we t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Believe me, dude, it's better we talk about something else."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me more about this *music pla..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me more about this *music place* you've been planning in the church."

fields.Title: You: ""Everyone's just mooching off the e..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Everyone's just mooching off the entrepreneurial class. Shackling the *doers*."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Go ahead...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Go ahead..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Wow. Social justice really matters..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wow. Social justice really matters that much to you? That's commendable. It really had you shaken up there... are you *sure* that's it, though?"
fields.Alternate1: "So, the thing that's got you crying in front of strangers... is social justice?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Man, that's because my equipment's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Man, that's because my equipment's on the ground."

fields.Title: Acele: ""I can't believe this turned into a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can't believe this turned into another Mike thing... Fine, okay, I'll stick to it." She takes the device from you and places it in her lap. "I'll knock it out in three rounds."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Oh, really?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, really?"

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, I guess I'll fuck off then."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, I guess I'll fuck off then." [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: ""Don't we have a bit of a logical i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't we have a bit of a logical inconsistency here? A categorical *no"* and a conditional *no*? Poor logic is a good sign of *lies*."

fields.Title: Acele: "She looks up, not entirely sure wha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She looks up, not entirely sure what that means.

fields.Title: You: ""What happens in the tent stays in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happens in the tent stays in the tent."

fields.Title: Empathy: "The kid isn't arrogant, she's just..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The kid isn't arrogant, she's just afraid to look you in the eye. You already put her in her place.

fields.Title: You: "(Kick some snow into her face with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Kick some snow into her face with your boot.) "You did NOT just speak like that to the police."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Crying helps, though. Get it out o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Crying helps, though. Get it out of your system and then maybe we can talk, okay? I'll be here."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm sorry you have to sit here on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm sorry you have to sit here on this coast, feeling miserable. At your age -- or at any age -- in this place... waiting for it to get dark."
fields.Alternate1: "I'm sorry you have to sit here in the damp church with the drugs wearing off. At your age -- or at any age -- in this place... waiting for it to get dark."

fields.Title: Acele: ""All right," she concedes. "My fath..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right," she concedes. "My father was a Zemylaki. He died years ago. He was a bad man. Not a lot of good things to say about him and what he did."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Not in person, but I let them know..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Not in person, but I let them know. You can't do anything without the fat ones getting wind. It wasn't too difficult to convince them, really..."

fields.Title: You: ""Oh, hmm, I can imagine what follow..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, hmm, I can imagine what followed after."

fields.Title: Acele: ""What do you think? The competition..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you think? The competition came and took everything away. It was like in a war zone..." She's gritting her teeth.

fields.Title: Acele: ""This?" She taps on the electronic..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This?" She taps on the electronic device. "Yeah, it's a portable recording device. For field recording. Low quality, but still."

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Everyone knows drugs make you invul..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Everyone knows drugs make you invulnerable to cold. You bet this one likes to *party*.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You." The lieutenant turns to you...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You." The lieutenant turns to you. "If you were intending to use an unorthodox questioning technique for this branch of the investigation -- which, by the way, is tangential at best -- you should have let me in on it."

fields.Title: You: ""What's that device you have there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's that device you have there?"
fields.Alternate1: "Let's talk about your contact mic again."

fields.Title: You: ""Actually, that's it for now." [Lea..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Actually, that's it for now." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, man," she nods. "That's why..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, man," she nods. "That's why you were crying over a hat, yelling about regaining your authority. National pride."
fields.Alternate1: "So, the thing that's got you crying in front of strangers is... national pride?"

fields.Title: You: ""First, they had just the faintest..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "First, they had just the faintest scent of chewing gum on them. I could still smell it under the... shit."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Okay, of course... What did you wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, of course... What did you want to know?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Man, when I get hurt I just wanna..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Man, when I get hurt I just wanna forget that shit, you know? That kind of selective memory."

fields.Title: Acele: ""How come you don't remember though..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "How come you don't remember though? Is it, like, some *selective memory* thing?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Diamorphine? But that hasn't been..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Diamorphine? But that hasn't been around for years -- five or more, like, seven years maybe? Everybody just does *hunch* now."

fields.Title: You: ""Yes, and we have some questions fo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, and we have some questions for you."

fields.Title: Acele: ""My 'associates'?" She blows on her..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My 'associates'?" She blows on her chilled fingers. "I haven't got much to say about them."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, kinda. I'm the head of the o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, kinda. I'm the head of the operation. Coordinated it with the Débardeurs, else they might get... unhappy."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Excuse me?" She casually brushes h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Excuse me?" She casually brushes her hand through her hair.
fields.Alternate1: "Excuse me?" She casually brushes some snow off her sleeve.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Who doesn't just *love* drugs? All..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who doesn't just *love* drugs? All the drugs." The lieutenant's voice is flat, although with a seeming undertone of sarcasm.

fields.Title: You: ""Considering what we're trying to d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Considering what we're trying to do here this doesn't look like a good sign."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Gee, thanks. Now, was there anythi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Gee, thanks. Now, was there anything else on your mind?"

fields.Title: You: ""Gotcha. I have some questions for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Gotcha. I have some questions for you."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Hard-cop." She nods to you with re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hard-cop." She nods to you with respect and turns off her recording device.

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah. No one understands that some..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah. No one understands that sometimes you've got to make sacrifices for the sake of progress. It's all very distressing."

fields.Title: You: ""Don't get me wrong, I'm all for sl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't get me wrong, I'm all for slow and steady progress. I just wish people would be a little more *reasonable*, is all."

fields.Title: Acele: ""I'm sorry I said 'fuck the hat.' I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm sorry I said 'fuck the hat.' I was concentrating on something else..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, well..." She tries to think..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, well..." She tries to think of something to say, but can't. "Look man, fuck the hat."

fields.Title: Acele: ""You know, that sounds kinda nice...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You know, that sounds kinda nice..."

fields.Title: You: ""You seem surprisingly comfortable..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You seem surprisingly comfortable with being questioned. Why's that?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""So, like..." The girl on the ice l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So, like..." The girl on the ice looks up at you. "Seriously, what's eating you, man?"

fields.Title: You: ""Really? That many?! Reduces me to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Really? That many?! Reduces me to tears thinking of the 3.6 billion and god knows how many more in that Seol place, crushed under the tyranny of the market."

fields.Title: You: ""Come to think of it -- the *whore*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Come to think of it -- the *whore* could have written them to her *lover*!"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He rolls his collar down to normal..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He rolls his collar down to normal human level and pulls out his familiar notebook. "We're from the police, by the way."

fields.Title: You: ""Too many millions to even know, al..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Too many millions to even know, all squashed under the tyranny of the market. It's terrible!"

fields.Title: You: ""You must be Acele.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You must be Acele."

fields.Title: You: ""The others told me you went inside..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The others told me you went inside the church. What did you see in there?"

fields.Title: You: ""Now. I have some questions for you.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Now. I have some questions for you."

fields.Title: You: ""GIVE YOU A LITTLE... ICE-COP-HAT-F..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "GIVE YOU A LITTLE... ICE-COP-HAT-FUCK-SHOW?!"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I didn't mean to, I'm sorry..." Th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't mean to, I'm sorry..." The girl is visibly shaken.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Two figures on the spring ice. One,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Two figures on the spring ice. One, a young woman, tries her best to ignore the other, a middle-aged man with spectacular sideburns, jumping up and down on the sea ice...

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Two figures on the spring ice. One,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Two figures on the spring ice. One, a young woman, tries her best to ignore the other, a middle-aged man with bloated cheeks, jumping up and down on the sea ice...

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Three figures on the spring ice. On..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Three figures on the spring ice. One, a shortish man, is standing with his shoulders slightly hunched. Another, a young woman, tries her best to ignore the third, a middle-aged man with bloated cheeks, jumping up and down on the sea ice...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant is watching the scen..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant is watching the scene unfold before his eyes, unsure how to react.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant is watching the scen..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant is watching the scene unfold before his eyes, unsure how to react.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Two figures on the spring ice. One,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Two figures on the spring ice. One, a young woman, tries her best to ignore the other, a middle-aged man with bloated cheeks, who's screaming at her with all his might...

fields.Title: Acele: "Looking up she sees a grown man --..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Looking up she sees a grown man -- on the wrong side of forty, his face bloated from alcohol and god knows what else -- not so quietly crying.

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, it's an odd hobby, but who a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, it's an odd hobby, but who am I to judge."

fields.Title: Acele: ""But that's not really what I wante..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But that's not really what I wanted to talk about. I wanted to thank you instead."

fields.Title: Shivers: "High above and to the east, the col..."
fields.Dialogue Text: High above and to the east, the cold winds blow over the feathers of an early songbird. She lands on the stone ledge of a tall building. Her beak a silvery grey.

fields.Title: You: ""Are you sure about that? What abou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Are you sure about that? What about this drug lab plan?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""It's a good thing you ended that m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's a good thing you ended that mess, though. I felt I was turning dad-wise, into a corrupt business-person. Unpleasant."

fields.Title: Acele: "Acele stares at him blankly. Two un..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Acele stares at him blankly. Two unflinching stares in collision course.

fields.Title: Acele: "She shrugs, obviously eager to go b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She shrugs, obviously eager to go back to whatever she's doing.

fields.Title: You: ""I just need a few minutes of your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I just need a few minutes of your time. Police business."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Oh, hello there.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, hello there."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""I'm listening." A cold wind blows..."]
You: ""Dear child, it's freezing. Where's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Dear child, it's freezing. Where's your hat?"

fields.Title: You: ""It's nice. You should wear one, to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's nice. You should wear one, too, if you plan on staying outside in this weather."

fields.Title: You: ""The Hat Law.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The Hat Law."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Wow, man." She raises her eyebrow...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wow, man." She raises her eyebrow. "That's pretty symbolic, don't you think?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""You're welcome." She thinks for a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're welcome." She thinks for a second, stretching her jaw. "Might be for the best to keep that shit forgotten though. Just my opinion. If it itches, don't scratch."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "For some reason, the words don't co..."
fields.Dialogue Text: For some reason, the words don't come out. Instead you instinctively touch your collar to check your necktie.

fields.Title: Drama: "He's really shaking and everything!"
fields.Dialogue Text: He's really shaking and everything!

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, or it might just be psych bu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, or it might just be psych bullshit, you know? Königstein wank."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""Well, it's just questioning, right..."]
You: ""Your associates tried to use me to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Your associates tried to use me to set up a drug lab. I'm guessing you knew of this plan."
fields.Alternate1: "Yes, your associates tried to use me to set up a drug lab and I'm guessing you knew of their plan."

fields.Title: Acele: "She's waiting."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's waiting.

fields.Title: Acele: "She looks up with a pained expressi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She looks up with a pained expression, her face caked with a thick layer of make up. With her left hand she's wiping some of it off to get the snow out of her face.

fields.Title: You: ""IS THAT HOW YOU SEE ME?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "IS THAT HOW YOU SEE ME?"

fields.Dialogue Text: Feels like you missed something here. What was that about a bird? Forget it. Maybe later.

fields.Dialogue Text: "Aren't there any local authorities who might look down on such activities?"

fields.Title: Composure: "She's attempting to remain calm, bu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's attempting to remain calm, but the phrase made her flinch.

fields.Title: You: ""And the law says you have to wear..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, I heard you, but what do you..."

fields.Alternate1: "No way! You have no idea how many taxes there *really* are -- you've never paid any! There are all these disguised, invisible taxes. Look, there's one right now!" (Point to the stained glass window.)

fields.Title: You: ""Yes, I found that to be very symbo..."

fields.Dialogue Text: "What is...?" Her shoulders shake a little.

fields.Alternate1: "I'm sorry you have to sit here on the ice with the drugs wearing off. At your age -- or at any age -- in this weather... waiting for it to get dark."

fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry?" She looks confused.

fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll help you all right."

fields.Dialogue Text: "Will you help us?"

fields.Dialogue Text: It's not that she has to run around and make money, it's more like she's concerned about her well-being. It is also not entirely because she's afraid of you. You can't really put your finger on it.

fields.Dialogue Text: "When I was sixteen I used to date this guy who had a limp. But it only showed when he was sober, so I guess it wasn't real or something. I don't know." She shrugs, eyes glazed over...

fields.Alternate1: "No-no." She cuts you off before you can finish the sentence. "I actually wanted to thank you. For getting me and my friends in here."

fields.Dialogue Text: "Gotcha."

fields.Title: You: ""That's nice to hear. You kids are..."

fields.Dialogue Text: Why does that melody sound so familiar?

fields.Dialogue Text: "And the wires?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "What is a *contact microphone*?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh huh, and you're sure it's social progress you're distressed about and not, I don't know, some chick?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm done here." [Leave.]
fields.Alternate1: "We're done here." [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: ""So keep that in mind while I ask s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So keep that in mind while I ask some questions."

fields.Dialogue Text: "What are we even talking about?"

fields.Title: You: ""Exactly. I don't wanna talk about..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Exactly. I don't wanna talk about it."

fields.Title: You: ""How many people are there in the w..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah, that's pretty bad," she nods..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, that's pretty bad," she nods. "Are you sure you're not just hung up on some chick though?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Used to be sweet, now it's shit --..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Used to be sweet, now it's shit -- seems pretty symbolic to me. Anyway, what else?

fields.Title: You: ""You know, I'm not sure this made t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You know, I'm not sure this made things any better."

fields.Title: Acele: ""What's *smack*?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's *smack*?"

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, she seems legitimately confus..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, she seems legitimately confused. Tell her what this *D* is."

fields.Title: You: ""Nothing, if you got this. Don't be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nothing, if you got this. Don't be scared."

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah, I can tell this was once a p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, I can tell this was once a proud nation. Now all this internationalist bullshit has brought Revachol to its knees."

fields.Title: You: ""Maybe we should get acquainted, th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe we should get acquainted, then?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Where do I start?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where do I start?"

fields.Title: You: ""Oh, I see. I'm not good enough for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, I see. I'm not good enough for the lady. She's accustomed to more gentlemanly folk. Well, so be it." [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: ""Why would anyone do that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why would anyone do that?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Sorry. I just don't tell people ab..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry. I just don't tell people about my friends and who they are and so on. I don't provide information on them."

fields.Dialogue Text: "O pasăre de argint."

fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm listening." A cold wind blows in from the sea. She breathes on her fingers for warmth, looking up at you.

fields.Title: You: ""I said, you should have a hat on.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I said, you should have a hat on."

fields.Dialogue Text: "We have nothing left to do but hope this *was* a play on your part -- and to move on. Now." He turns to the young woman. "We have some questions for you."

fields.Title: You: ""Um, yeah, and I would like to ask..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Um, yeah, and I would like to ask some questions now. So, questions."

fields.Dialogue Text: Something about the way she says it makes you think she's not bothered by any of the cop-show questioning.

fields.Title: Horrific Necktie: "It's crooked again, it always is. I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's crooked again, it always is. It's a traffic accident and a noose. Also, you should ask if she wants to party. Or better yet, ask her about that hat! Lest the necktie think you're boring...

fields.Dialogue Text: C'mon. She must have known it the moment you walked up to her.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Sorry, mister, I don't really do d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry, mister, I don't really do drugs. Especially with people I just met."

fields.Title: Acele: ""I, like, saw you go into the tent...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I, like, saw you go into the tent. It's right there."

fields.Title: Acele: "She gathers herself for a moment, t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She gathers herself for a moment, then says, "Okay."

fields.Dialogue Text: "RIGHT HERE ON THE SEA ICE?!"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I didn't mean to, I'm sorry..." Th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't mean to, I'm sorry..." The girl is visibly shaken.

fields.Title: Authority: "Lots of feeling. Feel it up, *way*..."

fields.Dialogue Text: Three figures on the spring ice. One, a shortish man, is standing with his shoulders slightly hunched. Another, a young woman, tries her best to ignore the third, a middle-aged man with spectacular sideburns, jumping up and down on the sea ice...

fields.Title: Acele: ""This... isn't really about the hat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This... isn't really about the hat, is it?"

fields.Title: You: ""How's everyone doing?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "How's everyone doing?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""So after his death we had nothing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So after his death we had nothing left. And we were in danger. My mother had to change her name, mine too. We left it all behind."

fields.Dialogue Text: "'Left it all behind.' Are you sure you did?" The lieutenant narrows his eyes at the girl. "Who can tell with all the delinquent behaviour?"

fields.Title: You: ""I doubt that. You're probably up t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I doubt that. You're probably up to no good."

fields.Dialogue Text: "So, you wanna *party*?"

fields.Dialogue Text: It's cold out here, but she's not wearing a hat! She must be freezing.

fields.Dialogue Text: "You and I both, although... I don't have to *imagine*. The competition came and took everything away. It was like in a war zone..." She's gritting her teeth.

fields.Title: You: ""Alright, I got some questions for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Alright, I got some questions for you."

fields.Title: You: ""Why would anyone do that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why would anyone do that?"

fields.Title: Acele: "The shaggy-haired girl kneels on th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The shaggy-haired girl kneels on the sea ice. She looks up as you approach.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Shoot." A cold wind blows. She bre..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shoot." A cold wind blows. She breathes on her hands for warmth.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes, what *do* you mean?" The lieu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, what *do* you mean?" The lieutenant sounds serious.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Oh, of course." She doesn't sound..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, of course." She doesn't sound surprised.

fields.Title: You: ""Questions, right! I had some for y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Questions, right! I had some for you."

fields.Title: You: ""Yup. Next to nothing.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yup. Next to nothing."

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah, I'm sure. Why would I have r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, I'm sure. Why would I have reacted so strongly otherwise?"

fields.Title: Perception: "Her hair is dyed blonde, with dark..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her hair is dyed blonde, with dark roots showing, and she wears thick black eye-liner. Most men wouldn't call her pretty -- there is a manliness to her. A coarseness.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Tryin'a score some *dope*, man. Li..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tryin'a score some *dope*, man. Like we planned. Tryin'a score some smack -- you got any?" He hops from one foot to the other in anticipation.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Hunch is like ten times stronger t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hunch is like ten times stronger than diamorphine and *waaay* more lethal. I think the name is... B-hydroxy-something."

fields.Title: You: ""The people who built this world in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The people who built this world intended it to be better for you, but they failed. It is easier to live in their failure with this by your side." (Tap on the tape recorder.)

fields.Title: Authority: "There is little you can do to help..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is little you can do to help her now, but given the chance you feel like you *should*. There is something about her. A weightiness.

fields.Title: Shivers: "Long shadows, short shadows. Quiet..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Long shadows, short shadows. Quiet shadows of local children, loud shadows drunks and also a shadow made of sticks... you breathe on your hands for warmth.

fields.Title: You: ""What's your name?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's your name?"

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah, people just can't get off th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, people just can't get off their asses -- zero hireable talent in this city. Zero. No wonder everyone's poor as potatoes."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Oh, really?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, really?"

fields.Title: Logic: "Why would a categorical *no* need a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Why would a categorical *no* need a conditional *no* to support it?

fields.Title: You: ""I didn't see a case in the church..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't see a case in the church story."

fields.Title: Acele: "She looks down, pretending to be bu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She looks down, pretending to be busy with the device.

fields.Title: Acele: ""You know, you're not the only one..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You know, you're not the only one with issues." There's a motherly hint to her voice. "I self-medicate, shit... life's a horror, you know."
fields.Alternate1: "Okay, sure. You're not the only one with issues." There's a motherly hint to her voice. "I self-medicate, shit... life's a horror, you know."

fields.Title: Acele: ""This?" She taps on the electronic..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This?" She taps on the electronic device. "Yeah, it's a portable recording device. For field recording. Low quality, but still."

fields.Title: Acele: ""He bought the family a huge house,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He bought the family a huge house, so we got to live... at least temporarily... in a giant *castle* in Jamrock. And then he died."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yes, better that way...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, better that way..."

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah, no, don't worry, I was just..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, no, don't worry, I was just saying... I don't mind drugs, I'm all into drugs myself, yeah, drugs."

fields.Title: You: ""You're Acele.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're Acele."

fields.Title: Authority: "What did she just say? That's not h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What did she just say? That's not how a civilian is supposed to address an officer of the law.

fields.Title: You: ""People just keep putting their sel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "People just keep putting their selfish interests ahead of the greater good."
